## üìã **Sprint 5 vs Sprint 6 Support**

### **Sprint 5 Implementation (POC) ‚úÖ**
```xml
<!-- SUPPORTED: RS232 only -->
<port number="1">
  <protocol>rs232</protocol>
  <speed>115200</speed>
  <data_pattern>n81</data_pattern>
  <!-- 3-phase commands supported -->
</port>
```

### **Sprint 6 Expansion Plan üöÄ**
```xml
<!-- PLANNED: All 6 protocols -->
<port number="1"><protocol>rs232</protocol></port>  <!-- ‚úÖ Sprint 5 -->
<port number="2"><protocol>rs485</protocol></port>  <!-- üöÄ Sprint 6 -->
<port number="3"><protocol>usb</protocol></port>    <!-- üöÄ Sprint 6 -->
<port number="4"><protocol>can</protocol></port>    <!-- üöÄ Sprint 6 -->
<port number="5"><protocol>i2c</protocol></port>    <!-- üöÄ Sprint 6 -->
<port number="6"><protocol>spi</protocol></port>    <!-- üöÄ Sprint 6 -->
```

